	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00">記得有一次，<delay20 /><snpcAnim id="TkkEh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />
我曾經夢到<delay8 />
與這裡十分相似的無人島<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聽說這裡<delay8 />之前也是無人島呢，<delay frames="30" />
<snpcAnim id="TkkQuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />難不成我那次<delay20 />
是真的夢到這裡了。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這裡的人和這整座島都充滿活力，<delay20 />
<snpcAnim id="TkkNodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />很多同伴都想聚過來這裡，<delay frames="40" />
<snpcAnim id="TkkQuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也感受到這股魅力喔。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00"><snpcAnim id="TkkEh" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不好意思，<delay20 />
