	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00">時間也差不多了，<delay20 />
<snpcAnim id="TkkNodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />準備開始表演吧。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00"><snpcAnim id="TkkEh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那麼，<delay8 />我將為<delay frames="30" />
