<snpcAnim id="TkkQuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />獻上一首<10_5 /><colour id="1" />大家集合吧<colour id="65535" /><endTag a="10" b="5" />。<10_7 arg="150" /></message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00"><snpcAnim id="TkkNodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />非常感謝大家。<delay frames="45" />
<snpcAnim id="TkkQuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那麼，<delay20 />我們下次見。<10_8 arg="75" /></message>
